                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.9311/358b: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-10-12T12:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 12, 1928—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>346. I am informed by the Chinese Minister that the proposal is made by his
                    Government that the Chinese Legation here and the American Legation and several
                    others in Peking be made embassies. A statement of your views by cable would be
                    welcomed by me.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
